definitions.definition: Relating to or resembling the stars ; starry .

Composed of ethereal material or non-physical (sometimes supersensible ), and capable of sometimes separating from the physical body (as an astral body ) to travel to other places or to other realms of existence (in or via the astral plane ).

main_definition: Relating to or resembling the stars ; starry .
secondary_definitions: ( parapsychology , theosophy , fantasy ) Composed of ethereal material or non-physical (sometimes supersensible ), and capable of sometimes separating from the physical body (as an astral body ) to travel to other places or to other realms of existence (in or via the astral plane ).
